data.description: This single-owner gem, situated on an oversized lot within the gated community of Bella Vida in Cape Coral, presents a captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, one-story home that is a must-see!  The residence features an inviting open floorplan, accentuated by a spacious living room that offers views of the picturesque lake, where you often see others fishing. Throughout the home, you'll find both tile and carpet flooring.  The primary suite has views of the lake and includes 2 walk-in closets and a stunning bathroom with updated fixtures, featuring his and her sinks, a stand-alone shower, and an indulgent garden tub.  For your convenience, a generator with permitted hookup is included in the sale, and the possibility of including some furniture is open for negotiation.  Bella Vida is perfectly located, granting easy access to shopping, dining, beaches, and the myriad attractions that make Southwest Florida living exceptional. This community also boasts an array of fantastic amenities, including a resort-style pool, sports courts, a playground, and much more. Bring your golf cart and fishing poles!  X flood zone! No flood insurance needed!
